    "33236823": {
      "title": "Rab GTPases as coordinators of vesicle traffic",
      "abstract": "Rab GTPases control intracellular vesicle traffic by acting as regulatable switches that recruit effector molecules when in their GTP-bound form. The functional coupling between multiple Rab GTPases ensures the spatiotemporally coordinated regulation of vesicle traffic."
